#: ../../backend/3fs.md:1
msgid ""
"RTP LLM supports using 3FS for persistent caching of KVCache, providing a"
" secondary cache for KVCache."
msgstr "RTP-LLM 支持使用 3FS 对 KVCache 进行持久化缓存，为 KVCache 提供二级缓存。"

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:3
msgid ""
"When model computational complexity is high or GPU memory is "
"insufficient, the already computed KVCache can be offloaded to 3FS and "
"reused in subsequent inference from the KVCache stored in 3FS, reducing "
"TTFT (Time To First Token); at the same time, GPU memory computing "
"resources can also be freed up for other uses."
msgstr "当模型计算复杂度较高或 GPU 内存不足时，已计算的 KVCache 可以卸载到 3FS 中，并在后续推理中复用 3FS 中存储的 KVCache，从而减少 TTFT（首 token 生成时间）；同时，GPU 内存计算资源也可以释放用于其他用途。"

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:5
msgid ""
"The framework integrates using the 3FS Native Client (USRBIO API) "
"approach to improve KVCache read and write performance."
msgstr "框架集成了 3FS Native Client (USRBIO API) 方式，以提升 KVCache 的读写性能。"

