"by following these steps:"
msgstr "目前，3FS 在生产环境中默认关闭。您可以通过以下步骤启用 3FS："

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:15
msgid ""
"3FS is currently only used in CUDA environments. During compilation, 3FS "
"needs to be actively compiled, and 3FS needs to be actively enabled at "
"runtime."
msgstr "3FS 目前仅在 CUDA 环境中使用。在编译时需要主动编译 3FS，并且在运行时需要主动启用 3FS。"

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:23
msgid "Business containers need to add the following configuration:"
msgstr "业务容器需要添加以下配置："

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:39
msgid ""
"Note: The shm size needs to be calculated. One TP requires 8GB (4GB for "
"reading and 4GB for writing). For 4TP, 3FS requires 32GB of shm. Other "
"services also occupy some shm, so it's set to 40GB here. Additionally, "
"the memory size applied for by the business cannot be lower than this shm"
" size."
msgstr "注意：shm 大小需要计算。一个 TP 需要 8GB（4GB 用于读取，4GB 用于写入）。对于 4TP，3FS 需要 32GB 的 shm。其他服务也会占用一些 shm，因此这里设置为 40GB。此外，业务申请的内存大小不能低于此 shm 大小。"

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:43
msgid "Add RDMA loopback prevention label:"
msgstr "添加 RDMA 回环预防标签："

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:55
msgid "Add environment variables or args at startup:"
msgstr "在启动时添加环境变量或参数："

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:67
msgid "Perform some validation after the container starts:"
msgstr "容器启动后执行一些验证："

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:69
msgid "After the container is up, verify that the 3fs directory exists:"
msgstr "容器启动后，验证 3fs 目录是否存在："

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:75
msgid "Verify that the shm size is correct:"
msgstr "验证 shm 大小是否正确："

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:81
msgid ""
"Check if /dev/shm is the requested size, such as 40GB. If not, confirm "
"that the total memory requested is not less than 40GB, as shm cannot be "
"smaller than the total memory requested by the pod."
msgstr "检查 /dev/shm 是否为申请的大小，例如 40GB。如果不是，请确认申请的总内存不少于 40GB，因为 shm 不能小于 pod 申请的总内存。"

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:85
msgid "Deployment Method"
msgstr "部署方式"

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:87
msgid ""
"Considering the group's RDMA network architecture, there will be RDMA "
"performance loss when communicating between different network clusters, "
"so currently one network cluster deploys a separate 3FS storage cluster."
msgstr "考虑到集团的 RDMA 网络架构，在不同网络集群之间通信时会有 RDMA 性能损失，因此目前每个网络集群部署独立的 3FS 存储集群。"

#: ../../backend/3fs.md:89
msgid ""
"3FS has already been deployed in HPAI NA61, NA175, Kingsoft Cloud, and "
"Beijing Lingjun data centers. Deployment in other data centers is "
"ongoing."
msgstr "3FS 已在 HPAI NA61、NA175、金山云和北京灵骏数据中心部署。其他数据中心的部署正在进行中。"

